version_description:
Now with over 100 Oldies Stations!

*** Big Update ***
- Updated Station List
- Improved Functionality
- Background Audio Controls (Next, Back, Play, Stop)

Follow us @MobyPixel on Twitter & Facebook to get news and updates!

Thanks & Enjoy,
Nick

Now with over 100 Oldies Stations!

• Day and Night mode—Easier to read text for anytime of day
• VoiceOver Optimized—We are pleased to have this version fully accessible for blind and low vision users
• Support for new screen resolutions—Check out the new look
• Various upgrades and improvements

If you get a chance, please leave a review for the new version--It really does help!

Thanks!
Nick
